            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is golden, add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong>,<strong> garlic</strong>,<strong> ginger</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1-2 min further or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>cornflour </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
