            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> black bean stock</strong> and <strong>mangetout</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 3-4 min or until the sauce has begun to thicken and the mangetout has slightly softened – this is your <strong>black bean chicken & mangetout stir-fry</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
