            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>black bean chicken & mangetout stir-fry </strong>with the<strong> cooked</strong> <strong>rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
